OL,10,FWhat is an energy price cap?
OL,12,FThe price cap was first introduced by
OL,13,Fenergy regulator Ofgem on 1 January,
OL,14,F2019.
OL,16,FIt is intended to protect against
OL,17,Fovercharging by limiting the amount
OL,18,Fthat suppliers can charge for each
OL,19,Funit of gas and electricity - measured
OL,20,Fin kWh (kilowatt hours).
